book.title: Dead Until Dark (Sookie Stackhouse #1)
book.description: Storyline: Dead Until Dark (Sookie Stackhouse #1) \n Sookie Stackhouse is just a small-time cocktail waitress in small-town Louisiana. Until the vampire of her dreams walks into her life-and one of her coworkers checks out.... Maybe having a vampire for a boyfriend isn't such a bright idea.\n
book.author: Charlaine Harris
